summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3413 for the improvement of 50th Avenue South, from Cloverdale Street to Henderson Street, all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 42308, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
